    "body": "@dapplion  right now lodestar follows the spec to have `seenTTL` as 385s (`=550 * 0.7s`) https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/1f1ef67a06a9332db1b524ad1ac1f2a1ae05c2bf/packages/beacon-node/src/network/gossip/gossipsub.ts#L104\r\n\r\nthat's equivalent to `32 slots (propagation range)` * `12 SECONDS_PER_SLOT` + `2 * MAXIMUM_GOSSIP_CLOCK_DISPARITY_SEC (0.5s)` which is perfect to filter duplicate gossip attestations in the last 32 slots",
